@startuml
title Employee Initiating Chat Sequence Diagram

actor Employee
participant ChatClient
participant ChatServer
participant Customer

Employee -> ChatClient: Clicks on chat button
ChatClient -> ChatServer: Establish connection request
ChatServer -> Customer: New chat request from Employee
Customer -> ChatServer: Accepts chat request
ChatServer --> ChatClient: Connection established
Employee -> ChatServer: Sends initial message
ChatServer --> Customer: Employee's initial message
Customer --> ChatServer: Responds to Employee's message
ChatServer --> ChatClient: Customer's response
@enduml
